index_struct.text: This code file provides efficient data structures for keyword table indices. It includes three classes: GPTKeywordTableIndex, GPTSimpleKeywordTableIndex, and GPTRAKEKeywordTableIndex. The GPTKeywordTableIndex class is used to store and retrieve data from keyword tables, the GPTSimpleKeywordTableIndex class is used to store and retrieve data from simple keyword tables, and the GPTRAKEKeywordTableIndex class is used to store and retrieve data from keyword tables using the RAKE algorithm. These classes allow for quick retrieval of data from keyword tables, providing an efficient way to store and access data.
